:<font size="15">תּנּים</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
תּנּים   - תּנּין / tannîyn  tannîym / tan-neen', tan-neem'

===Etymology===
(The second form used in  {{KJVEze|29|3}}); intensive from the same as {{HH|8565}}; 

===Noun===
'''תּנּים'''

# A marine or land [[monster]], that is, sea serpent or jackal: - dragon, sea-monster, [[serpent]], [[whale]].

